<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="brand">Progress<span>Visualizer</span></h1>
        <p><strong>Quickly setup visual reporting for your <a href="http://www.trello.com" target="_blank">Trello</a> boards.</strong></p>
        <ol class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <h2 id="signup">Sign up</h2>
            <p>You need to create an account in order to associate your Trello account with ProgressVisualizer. See <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_policy_path %>.</p>
            <p>You can manage your existing account anytime from a drop down in the far right of the header.</p>
            <div>
              <div class="callout" style="margin-left:180px;width:120px;height:44px"></div>
              <%= image_tag("header-right.png", alt: "screenshot of header" )%>
            </div>
            <p><%= link_to("Sign up now", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default") %></p>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <h2 id="profile">Set up a profile</h2>
            <h3>Step 1</h3>
            <div>Create a reference to a specific trello board. Provide:</div>
            <ul>
              <li>A <strong>name</strong> that uniquely identifies this profile (you can have many profiles for one or more boards).</li>
              <li>Whether this profile is the <strong>default</strong> shown on log-in. You can switch profiles from a drop down in the header.
                <div>
                  <div class="callout" style="width:190px;height:44px"></div>
                  <%= image_tag("header-right.png", alt: "screenshot of header" )%>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>A <strong>read-only user token</strong> that represents your permission for ProgressVisualizer to read your trello data.
                <ul>
                  <li>Click the provided link to generate this token.
                    <div class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">
                      <div class="callout" style="margin-left:444px;width:160px;height:44px"></div>
                      <%= image_tag("user-token-field.png", alt: "user token field in create/edit user profile" )%>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li>Click the link and copy the resulting token (random string of characters) into the field provided.
                    <div class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">
                      <div class="callout" style="margin-left:105px;width:340px;height:44px"></div>
                      <%= image_tag("user-token-field.png", alt: "user token field in create/edit user profile" )%>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>The <strong>short board id</strong> of your Trello board. This is the random string that appears in the URL of your trello board, e.g. in the URL https://trello.com/b/WWtHBRod/progress-visualizer, the short board id is <strong>WWtHBRod</strong>.
                <div class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">
                  <%= image_tag("board-id-field.png", alt: "trello board short id field" )%>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Step 2</h3>
            <div>Set preferences for your trello board.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item"><h2>Start visualizing</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><h3>Burn up charts</h3></li>
              <li><h3>Yesterday's Weather</h3></li>
              <li><h3>Long term trend</h3></li>
              <li><h3>Done stories table</h3></li>
              <li><h3>Dashboard/Report</h3></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>